<div><div><h2>Q2 results: ITC profit up 12% to Rs 2,955 crore</h2></div><div>diversified group itc on friday reported a 11.92% rise in standalone net profit to rs 2954.67 crore for the quarter ended 30 september 2018. the company had posted a net profit of rs 2639.84 crore in the second quarter of 2017-18 itc said in filing to the bse. revenue from operations stood at rs 11272.51 crore compared with rs 9763.92 crore in the year-ago period. shares of itc were trading at rs 278.50 per scrip on the bse down 3.05% from the previous close.</div></div>